title: Mozart - 2 Piano Sonatas, Fantasie KV 397 - Pogorelich
description:
W. A. Mozart: Piano Sonatas KV 283 and 331, Fantasie KV 397.

Everyone probably already has his or her favourite complete Mozart sonatas recording already. But here are two beautiful sonatas and the Fantasie KV 397 played with refined distinction by Ivo Pogorelich. This CD was released by DG twenty years ago, in 1995.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
